Package: smriti
Title: Automated Routing Engine for Longitudinal Missing Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Xiyuan", "Guo", email = "tommyguo039@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An automated routing engine for longitudinal missing data. 
    It utilizes a Lagrange-constrained Random Forest based on sample size, 
    missingness rate, and skew to preserve structural variance.
